Updated 03/09/2015:

1. Each question will be written in HTML
2. Use multiple images and insert links
3. Apply “click” function to “Yes” “No” and “Continue”
4. Keep the same layout throughout the quiz

Different steps for fair trade coffee quiz:

1. Start menu
Start Quiz button that will take to first question

2. Automated pop-ups
Display “incorrect” pop up, when the thumbnail is clicked
Display “good job” pop up when the correct thumbnail is clicked

3. Moving on
Continue button at the bottom that can be clicked regardless of  the answer

4. Filling coffee cup
With every correct answer an, empty coffee maker gets a little more coffee
On the opposite side of the continue button
